title: ABBA - Love Stories (1998)(gnv64)
description:
Love Stories is a 1998 greatest hits compilation album of love songs released by Swedish pop group ABBA. 
It consists of seventeen songs, about half of which have been singles. 
The other half are album tracks taken from the albums Arrival, ABBA: The Album, Super Trouper, and The Visitors. 
It was promoted by SAT1 on German TV.
Love Stories replaces two old collection of ABBA's love songs, titled I Love ABBA and From ABBA With Love", 
both released in 1984 and deleted several years later.
